WEBVTT

00:02.595 --> 00:04.349
We can get in a car.

00:05.372 --> 00:06.812
We can drive away.

00:07.881 --> 00:09.353
We can get in a boat.

00:10.406 --> 00:12.081
We can sail away.

00:13.198 --> 00:14.933
We can get on a plane.

00:16.003 --> 00:17.646
We can fly away.

00:18.715 --> 00:20.344
We can get on a bike.

00:21.397 --> 00:23.084
We can pedal away.

00:24.091 --> 00:26.017
We can get in a balloon.

00:27.071 --> 00:28.622
We can float away.

00:29.550 --> 00:31.398
We can get on a train.

00:32.467 --> 00:34.064
We can chug away.

00:35.118 --> 00:36.771
We can get in a rocket.

00:37.840 --> 00:39.751
We can zoom away.

00:40.851 --> 00:42.964
We can put on our shoes.

00:43.986 --> 00:45.473
We can run away.

00:49.461 --> 00:51.591
How can we get to the airport?

00:52.597 --> 00:54.179
We can get in a car.

00:55.245 --> 00:57.547
How can we get to Jeju Island?

00:58.617 --> 01:00.276
We can get on a plane.

01:01.361 --> 01:02.989
Can we get to the moon?

01:04.021 --> 01:07.957
Of course. We can get to the moon in a rocket.

